damn it, has anybody ever really known what they wanted or has everyone always been confused? ...well my suspicions have been confirmed..i am not going to elaborate any farther b/c i kinda just dont feel like, the movies kicked some serious ass! i got to make out with kc, and nobody saw it..lmao, it was great..and my mom saw us kiss. funny stuff..yeah, so life sucks so bad right now, and bryan just called me a slacker..lol..like he has room to talk. but ne ways i really dont feel like writing anymore, so i will finish this with my newest quote--
" How long to I have to lye here dying, before you try and revive me?"

...what can i say my weekend was interesting, baby shower on saturday that sucked really bad no one remotely interesting was there and i just sat around and did nothing, better than having to work around my house i suppose,and the good part was well the only good part,i got to hear stories about my father fucked up child hood, (and i thought i was bad...not compared to him)things just keep going downhill for me idk i just feel..blah, i have lost the me,and i dont like it. but there is nothing i can do ,the home life is steadily going down hill, i mean yesterday, my dad hit us and when he hit my sister kendra he busted her lip open and just looked at it, said he didnt care ,and hit kara. i cant cope anymore nore do i want to, i did something..and i dont know if i will be able to stop,its a slow and painful addiction.and no i am not lookinf for sympathy or for someone to comment saying' i dont want you to be sad' or anythin b/c if i wanted that i would have used me other sc/n nope, i just wanted to get it out, say my peace, and not let this build up inside of me,it kills me sometimes to even think about it but its better to write than to keep this bottled up inside, right?

yep any of my friends who ever get on to this sc/n name it is i, cierra, this is a back up sc/n just in case my parents ever get on to lj, and they see this they will freak out and ill start laughing ....but yeah so this is just a back up. i dont use it...and wont less i have to.
